parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause the brake pedal to go to the floor, leading to loss of control, accidents, or property damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the ABS system can cause the vehicle to lose control, experience extended stopping distances, or collide with other vehicles or objects, leading to accidents or property damage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the upper intake manifold can cause coolant leaks, engine stalling, and in extreme cases, engine fires, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: white smoke emitting from under the hood

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the intake manifold gasket can cause coolant leaks, engine overheating, and engine damage, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: white smoke emitting from under the hood

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling and performance issues can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the vehicle stalls while driving at high speeds.
Oil leaks and engine damage can cause engine failure, accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
The sudden and unexpected deployment of airbags can cause injuries, including facial burns, bruises, and abrasions, and can also lead to accidents or loss of control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Airbag deployment without impact or crash
airbag light on the instrument panel
airbag hitting the driver or passenger in the face or abdomen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to more severe injuries or fatalities, as the occupants of the vehicle are not protected from the impact.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
including broken bones and facial injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Malfunctions in the airbag system can cause the airbag light to come on, indicating a problem, and can lead to inadvertent airbag deployment or failure of airbags to deploy in a crash.
symptoms: Airbag light on the instrument panel
rubbing noise from the steering column
airbag module coil and wire needing to be replaced.
